    Plot time series for each cluster with quantile bands for both scenario and control.

    Arguments:
        timeseries:      np.ndarray, shape (n_land_cells, time_steps) - scenario time series
        timeseries_ctrl: np.ndarray, shape (n_land_cells, time_steps) - control time series
        labels:          np.ndarray, shape (n_land_cells,)            - cluster assignment per cell
